":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of radio button"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for  "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"radios"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"like "},{"code":"OUDSRadioButton","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"OUDSRadioButtonItem","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide all tokens to the users."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"RadioButtonComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"radio buttons"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Radio buttons"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"code":"SizeSemanticToken","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":") and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"borders ("},{"code":"BorderRadiusSemanticToken","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"BorderWidthSemanticToken","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"These components share the same type of tokens which are all gathered here."}]}}}